{"tid":861223,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"頭先入lift好似聽到啲唔應該聽到既野","createTime":"2018-10-14T03:21:35.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-29T03:29:24.000Z","uid":59151,"like":27,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"8c2ef49489c427c2fa9f152823767a6cdde3eccb","tid":861223,"uid":59151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-14T03:21:35.000Z","msg":"我=<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n人妻=<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n呀叔=<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n場景：間lift得我地三個人 人妻同呀叔應該熟熟地 大家住既樓層都唔一樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n人妻： 咦 hello 好耐冇見啦喎 今排搞咩呀<br />\n呀叔： 哦 冇呀 未又係忙返工<br />\n人妻：我老公都係成日忙返工唔係屋企 <br />\n呀叔：我知 有聽佢講過下<br />\n人妻：唉 咁你又唔多啲上黎坐下 好得閒呀我<br />\n呀叔：（唔知係咪因為我係到佢就好尷尬咁笑左下）好啦 得閒先上黎<br />\n人妻：你忙咩姐 得閒未上黎坐囉<br />\n呀叔：...<br />\n呢個時候我就出左lift 有冇人知到底佢地係到講緊啲咩？"},{"pid":"4f09bbf6c381056bc26689da3459bfb27b118504","tid":861223,"uid":59497,"like":6,"dislike":41,"score":-35,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-14T03:23:46.000Z","msg":"你set左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 又唔用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c73729dc6162c44d1a80cec9abd983ca15803c05","tid":861223,"uid":129658,"like":16,"dislike":1,"score":15,"quote":{"pid":"4f09bbf6c381056bc26689da3459bfb27b118504","tid":861223,"uid":59497,"like":6,"dislike":41,"score":-35,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-14T03:23:46.000Z","msg":"你set左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 又唔用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-14T03:25:23.000Z","msg":"新會然<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=